{"tid":956172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務處刑事及保安處長李志恒北海道車禍　頸椎受傷","createTime":"2018-12-26T05:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T12:48:25.000Z","uid":79382,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e183bae1d3aadc6aa05e592d6f81fea4a0d22588","tid":956172,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"警務處刑事及保安處長李志恒北海道車禍　頸椎受傷<br />\n<br />\n警務處刑事及保安處長李志恒偕同妻子及親友，昨午於日本北海道小樽自駕遊時遇上車禍。據了解，出事汽車不是由李志恒駕駛，他的頸椎受傷，但並無生命危險。其妻及其他親友傷勢各異。<br />\n<br />\n李的胞兄弟知悉事件後，正趕往日本了解，警方亦派出福利官前往日本協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20181226/s00001/1545800260980/%e8%ad%a6%e5%8b%99%e8%99%95%e5%88%91%e4%ba%8b%e5%8f%8a%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%89%e8%99%95%e9%95%b7%e6%9d%8e%e5%bf%97%e6%81%92%e5%8c%97%e6%b5%b7%e9%81%93%e8%bb%8a%e7%a6%8d-%e9%a0%b8%e6%a4%8e%e5%8f%97%e5%82%b7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20181226%2Fs00001%2F1545800260980%2F%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258b%2599%25e8%2599%2595%25e5%2588%2591%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258f%258a%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25ae%2589%25e8%2599%2595%25e9%2595%25b7%25e6%259d%258e%25e5%25bf%2597%25e6%2581%2592%25e5%258c%2597%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e9%2581%2593%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%25a6%258d-%25e9%25a0%25b8%25e6%25a4%258e%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=71b53a91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20181226%2Fs00001%2F1545800260980%2F%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258b%2599%25e8%2599%2595%25e5%2588%2591%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258f%258a%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25ae%2589%25e8%2599%2595%25e9%2595%25b7%25e6%259d%258e%25e5%25bf%2597%25e6%2581%2592%25e5%258c%2597%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e9%2581%2593%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%25a6%258d-%25e9%25a0%25b8%25e6%25a4%258e%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7&h=ff4d994a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/2018